896
01:02:42,551 --> 01:02:44,845
Enjoy the rest of your meal.

897
01:03:30,933 --> 01:03:34,937
I ordered brisket on a roll with fries

898
01:03:35,562 --> 01:03:39,316
and two baskets of soda bread.
I know how you like that shit.

899
01:03:39,399 --> 01:03:41,276
Is that okay by you?

900
01:03:42,653 --> 01:03:46,323
Take a look at the guy at the table.
Take a good look.

901
01:03:57,584 --> 01:03:59,127
Motherfucker.

902
01:04:25,320 --> 01:04:26,780
That's him.

903
01:04:27,239 --> 01:04:29,491
Are you fucking kidding me?

904
01:04:32,286 --> 01:04:33,495
Bingo.

905
01:04:58,478 --> 01:05:00,147
This is amazing.

906
01:05:00,480 --> 01:05:02,816
Hello. It's been a long time.

907
01:05:04,276 --> 01:05:06,361
Who the fuck are you guys?

908
01:05:09,823 --> 01:05:11,742
Who the fuck asked you to sit down?

909
01:05:11,825 --> 01:05:15,621
I thought you'd be happy to see us.
I guess I was wrong.

910
01:05:16,830 --> 01:05:19,291
JOHN: I thought you'd do a lot better.

911
01:05:19,791 --> 01:05:22,753
With all that training,
all that time you put in,

912
01:05:22,836 --> 01:05:25,047
just to end up watching
someone else's money.

913
01:05:25,172 --> 01:05:26,340
That seems like a waste.

914
01:05:26,465 --> 01:05:28,550
For the last time,
what the fuck do you want?

915
01:05:28,675 --> 01:05:31,887
Why don't you take your time?
it'll come to you.

916
01:05:36,183 --> 01:05:38,560
I can see how he might forget us.

917
01:05:38,685 --> 01:05:41,647
We were just something
for you and your friends to play with.

918
01:05:41,730 --> 01:05:46,526
It's a little harder for us to forget.
You gave us so much more to remember.

919
01:05:49,821 --> 01:05:53,784
You can't quite place us, can you, chief?
Let me help you out.

920
01:05:53,867 --> 01:05:57,245
You're looking at John Reilly
and Tommy Marcano.

921
01:06:03,168 --> 01:06:04,378
Yeah.

922
01:06:07,381 --> 01:06:08,924
That's right.

923
01:06:15,389 --> 01:06:17,516
That was a long time ago.

924
01:06:19,893 --> 01:06:21,728
So, how you been?

925
01:06:21,895 --> 01:06:23,897
Yeah, we ain't kids now.

926
01:06:24,022 --> 01:06:26,066
So what do you want?

927
01:06:27,025 --> 01:06:30,070
What I've always wanted is to watch you die.

928
01:06:36,076 --> 01:06:38,120
TOMMY: You ordered the meatloaf.

929
01:06:38,912 --> 01:06:42,749
The brisket's really good here,
