930
01:06:43,041 --> 01:06:44,584
You fucked up.

931
01:06:57,764 --> 01:07:02,102
You were scared little pricks, both of you.

932
01:07:03,603 --> 01:07:07,816
All of you, scared shitless.

933
01:07:10,152 --> 01:07:13,739
I tried to make you tough.
I tried to make you hard.

934
01:07:13,822 --> 01:07:15,490
TOMMY: I had you all wrong then, Nokes.

935
01:07:15,615 --> 01:07:19,202
All this time I thought you just liked
fucking and beating up little boys.

936
01:07:19,286 --> 01:07:22,080
You two motherfuckers
are gonna burn in hell.

937
01:07:22,164 --> 01:07:25,292
-You're gonna burn in hell.
-Yeah, after you.

938
01:07:26,877 --> 01:07:28,211
(GASPING)

939
01:07:28,295 --> 01:07:30,255
(GROAN ING)I

940
01:07:30,338 --> 01:07:32,299
Did that hurt, Nokes?

941
01:07:57,657 --> 01:07:59,326
(CRYING)

942
01:08:08,835 --> 01:08:10,170
Jerry.

943
01:08:10,837 --> 01:08:14,382
Sorry, should've made
those brisket sandwiches to go.

